    <entry>
      <title>如何讓Yolla在Bluestacks內運行的&#39;小地球&#39;發出虛擬聲音？</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/17/study0416-01/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/17/study0416-01/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSumGSs7iIVcQfYX_LuXtAYqQ_12F1Jz6bYdQ&s"></p><p><strong>如何在 BlueStacks 5 上選擇不同的音訊設備</strong></p><p>這樣有什麼幫助？你可以在 BlueStacks 5 上選擇你喜歡的揚聲器（音訊輸出）和麥克風（音訊輸入）設備。能夠在不同的音訊設備之間進行選擇是非常有用的……<br>support.bluestacks.com</p><p><a href="https://support.bluestacks.com/hc/en-us/articles/4405388977549-How-to-choose-between-different-audio-devices-on-BlueStacks-5#:~:text=How%20can%20I%20switch%20between,click%20on%20%22Save%20changes%22.">在BlueStacks裡，麥克風設為虛擬聲卡。</a></p><p><a href="https://support.bluestacks.com/hc/en-us/articles/4405388977549-How-to-choose-between-different-audio-devices-on-BlueStacks-5#:~:text=How%20can%20I%20switch%20between,click%20on%20%22Save%20changes%22">https://support.bluestacks.com/hc/en-us/articles/4405388977549-How-to-choose-between-different-audio-devices-on-BlueStacks-5#:~:text=How%20can%20I%20switch%20between,click%20on%20%22Save%20changes%22</a>.</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
