        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Kevin’s-個人檔案"><a href="#Kevin’s-個人檔案" class="headerlink" title="Kevin’s 個人檔案"></a>Kevin’s 個人檔案</h2><h3 id="Project"><a href="#Project" class="headerlink" title="Project"></a>Project</h3><ul><li>Description:</li></ul><ol><li>可以抓取 Flickr 網站的圖片，抓全部相片和博覽館的圖片</li><li>可以抓取 Pinterest 的圖片</li><li>可以抓取 ppt網站的 Beauty, KoreaStar, KoreaDrama 的圖片<br>包括 Python 自動翻頁，禁止通知，抓取圖片的範圍等作法，selenium,requests,beautiful soup…API等工具</li></ol><h3 id="參考資料"><a href="#參考資料" class="headerlink" title="參考資料"></a>參考資料</h3><ul><li><a href="https://requests.readthedocs.io/en/latest/">Requests: HTTP for Humans™</a></li><li><a href="https://selenium-python-zh.readthedocs.io/en/latest/locating-elements.html">Selenium Python中文文檔</a></li><li><a href="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/python-programming-language-tutorial/?ref=outindfooter">Geeksforgeeks</a></li><li><a href="https://www.w3schools.com/python/default.asp">W3schools Python Tutorial</a></li><li><a href="https://hackmd.io/@aaronlife/python-topic-selenium">動態網頁爬蟲-使用Selenium</a></li><li><a href="https://hackmd.io/@aaronlife/python-topic-beautifulsoup#Python%E7%88%AC%E8%9F%B2%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Beautiful-Soup">Python爬蟲使用Beautiful Soup</a></li></ul><h1 id="Education"><a href="#Education" class="headerlink" title="Education"></a>Education</h1><ul><li><a href="https://www.nycu.edu.tw/nycu/ch/index">NYCU University</a></li><li><a href="https://www.ntou.edu.tw/">NTOU University</a></li></ul><h1 id="Work-Histroy"><a href="#Work-Histroy" class="headerlink" title="Work Histroy"></a>Work Histroy</h1><ul><li>Support Manager</li><li>Support Sr. Engineer</li><li></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
